eta_campaign/icons/icon_02.png</ThumbnailImage><xPower Type="GroupStart" GroupStart="" Name="IntroText" label="Intro Text" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false" Expanded="true"><IntroCopy type="dhtml" label="Intro Text" readonly="false" hidden="false" required="false"><![CDATA[<p>Search engines are a popular way to navigate the BYU-Idaho Web site.  But sometimes the results are out-of-date, duplicated, irrelevant, or  missing altogether. To address this, a Google search appliance has been  installed directly on campus. This new tool will continuously monitor  BYU-Idaho Web pages to provide the most timely search results.</p>
